        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女眼神浮现出一丝悲恸，她低头看向自己空空如也、残留着烧伤痕迹的手心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "除了自己，她什么都没有。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "繁华商场内，琳琅满目的商品在灯光下熠熠生辉，空气中飘荡着淡淡的香水味和新衣物的气息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "甜品店冷柜前，妮塔的脸紧贴在玻璃上，扁成一个滑稽的形状。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……这位客人，需不需要我帮您拿一块？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不要，我不买，我就看看。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔一边摇头，一边干脆地回答，丝毫不顾店员嘴角抽搐的样子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可你已经看了快五分钟了……这么犹豫，难不成又囊中羞涩了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿嘿……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔眼神闪烁，轻笑了两声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看她这副试图装傻蒙混过关的样子，我忍不住抬手，用指节轻轻敲了敲她的额头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿什么呢，之前赚的钱都到哪里去了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗷！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔捂住额头，发出小小的抗议声。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这不是攒着给分析员买礼物吗，总觉得上次那个金指虎还不够重。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唉~至于甜点嘛，吃不吃都行啦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一声叹息后，她低下头假装失落，嘴角却忍不住上扬，眼睛时不时偷瞄我的反应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说吧，想吃哪个？我给你买。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的话还没说完，妮塔就立刻招呼来店员，手指激动地戳在玻璃上，留下一小串模糊的指印。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个这个！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她指向的，是名字有些古怪，却十分畅销的招牌甜点“脏脏包”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恰如其名，面包表面杂乱地洒满了巧克力粉，看上去的确有些“脏兮兮”的样子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "店员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好的，请问需要切开吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不用不用，我要抱着啃！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接过脏脏包之后，妮塔满足地咬下一大口。她的脸颊立刻鼓了起来，像只满足的松鼠。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "很快，脏脏包被她递到我面前，咬开的缺口正好对着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你也来一口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "咬成这样才舍得给我一口？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哪有！这明明是最好吃的一口！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔急忙反驳，音调微微上扬，脸上还带着几分委屈的神色。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我重新看向她手上的甜点，才发现缺口处溢出了浓厚的巧克力，没了外层的包裹，香甜的气味轻易就飘了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "快咬啊！这一口下去包能吃到夹心！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在妮塔的百般示意下，我越过她留在上面的牙印，咬了下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "巧克力的香气瞬间就在嘴里扩散开来，浓郁而不腻人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "噗哈哈哈哈哈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道为什么，在我吞下面包后，妮塔开心地笑了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么了，突然笑得这么开心？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员~你的嘴角。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她伸手指了指自己的嘴角，示意着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我转向一旁的玻璃橱窗，自己的倒影清晰可见。果然，嘴角处有一块小小的、巧克力粉留下的污渍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "本想拿张纸巾擦拭干净，但全身上下的口袋找遍，却一无所获。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "忽然，妮塔倾身靠近我，唇贴上了我的嘴角，亲吻着那一小块巧克力痕迹，动作温柔而亲昵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一阵温热，我感受到她的舌尖轻轻划过，带走了那一点甜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不用麻烦找纸巾啦~这样不就好了，简单快捷！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔眨了眨眼睛，语气里满是得意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "确实是个好方法，下次也这样帮我清理下？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "昂？还有哪儿脏了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她先是一脸困惑，眉眼间透着清澈。在她很快理解我话中的意思后，脸噗嗤一下变得通红。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔不敢再看我，只是牵着我的手，视线投向别处，假装专心地啃着剩下的面包。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "时间差不多了，我们也该过去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "跟随路引，我们来到一处早就布置好的快闪场地，货架上摆放着数百个一模一样的牛皮纸袋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "据妮塔所说，这是商场为周年庆特地筹备的“盲盒活动”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一样价格买到的可能是普通水果，也可能是价值不菲的奢侈品。命运在每个纸袋里，都埋下了不同的“惊喜”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而妮塔的计划就是抽出最值钱的那个，然后转手卖掉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她对于这个计划可谓是志在必得……至于原因嘛，就得从上午说起了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从卡戎平台回来后，我难得拥有了一段悠闲时光。正在基地大厅享受咖啡时，妮塔鬼鬼祟祟靠了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "干什么！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的气音满含隐秘的兴奋，我也学着她的样子回应着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有好东西，跟我来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这样，妮塔拽上了我的手臂，把我往她的房间拖去。一路上，她左顾右盼，谨慎到了极点。",
        "disable": 0
